review: Very friendly and calm. Definitely recommend to visit him for any ailments. He will keep you at ease

Met this doc as my husband had shoulder pain and gastric issues which we didn't want to ignore. But completely unsatisfied with the doctor the way he checked (spoke for about 1min and not even exacturating) and directly suggested echo, ECG & Blood tests.  Also no suggestions no consultation on the life style or things to do.
